4
00:00:20,051 --> 00:00:22,027
我哥哥情况如何
I need to know about my brother.

5
00:00:22,077 --> 00:00:25,071
他还活着  快跑吧
He's alive. Get out now.

6
00:00:25,074 --> 00:00:28,097
他们很快就会意识到你就是幕后黑手了
It can't be long before they realize it's you.

7
00:00:29,001 --> 00:00:30,031
您快点回车里去
I need you to get back in the car.

8
00:00:33,007 --> 00:00:36,021
您的弟弟参与策划了这次炸弹袭击
Your brother was involved with the attack.

9
00:00:36,024 --> 00:00:38,051
他就是我们一直在找的内应
He's the insider we've been looking for.

10
00:00:38,054 --> 00:00:39,084
怎么回事
What's going on?

11
00:00:39,087 --> 00:00:41,064
尸体触发了危险物警报
The body triggered a Hazmat alarm.

12
00:00:41,067 --> 00:00:42,091
是高浓缩铀
It's highly enriched uranium.

13
00:00:42,094 --> 00:00:44,007
你的意思是它属于武器级别吗
You mean it's weapons-grade?

14
00:00:44,011 --> 00:00:45,067
他到底怎么会接触到这种物质的
How the hell did he come into contact with that?

15
00:00:45,071 --> 00:00:46,065
我想我知道怎么回事
I think I know the answer.

16
00:00:47,041 --> 00:00:49,091
有个持有武器级浓缩铀的人去找过我弟弟
Someone approached my brother with weapons-grade uranium.

17
00:00:49,094 --> 00:00:53,067
-谁  -此人能接触到前苏联废弃的核原料堆
- Who? - Someone who had access to decommissioned Soviet stockpile.

18
00:00:53,071 --> 00:00:57,051
你必须要在俄罗斯人把铀给我弟弟前找到他们
You must find the Russians before they can get the uranium to my brother.

19
00:00:57,054 --> 00:00:59,037
我要看你手里有浓缩铀棒的证据
I want proof that the rods exist,

20
00:00:59,037 --> 00:01:00,072
不然你休想得到钱
or you will not be paid.

21
00:01:00,072 --> 00:01:01,070
你要证据是吧
You want proof, huh?

22
00:01:03,004 --> 00:01:04,017
跟我来
Come with me.

23
00:01:04,021 --> 00:01:05,051
我的小儿子
My younger son,

24
00:01:05,054 --> 00:01:07,047
他负责运输浓缩铀棒
he was transporting the rods,

25
00:01:07,051 --> 00:01:08,081
但他太大意了
and he was careless.

26
00:01:08,084 --> 00:01:10,084
看到了吧  这就是你要的证据了
There, you have your proof.

27
00:01:10,087 --> 00:01:13,075
你在俄罗斯黑帮中做了近两年的卧底
You were undercover for nearly two years with the Russian mob.

28
00:01:15,020 --> 00:01:16,024
你的身份并未被揭穿
Your cover is still intact.

29
00:01:16,027 --> 00:01:18,067
你的意思是让我打回内部去吗
Are you asking me to go back in?

30
00:01:18,071 --> 00:01:21,011
沃克探员结束卧底工作已经六年多了
Agent Walker hasn't been undercover for over six years.

31
00:01:21,014 --> 00:01:23,011
我认为不应该让她来执行这个任务
I think you're making a mistake by putting her in.

32
00:01:23,014 --> 00:01:26,057
你一定还有其他选择
You must have other options.

33
00:01:26,061 --> 00:01:27,071
她是我们打入敌人内部的唯一途径
She's our only way in.

34
00:01:27,074 --> 00:01:28,087
那好  我跟她一起去
Fine, then I want to go with her.

35
00:01:28,091 --> 00:01:31,081
我猜你的计划是找人假扮成竞价的买主
I assume your plan is trying to set up a competing buy?

36
00:01:31,084 --> 00:01:33,001
就由我来假扮买主好了
I'll act as a buyer.

37
00:01:33,004 --> 00:01:35,041
我在找瓦德米尔
I'm looking for Vladimir.

38
00:01:35,044 --> 00:01:36,087
瓦德失踪了
Vlad disappeared.

39
00:01:36,091 --> 00:01:38,054
但你能找到他
But you can find him.

40
00:01:38,057 --> 00:01:40,054
他们每时每刻都知道我在哪儿
They know where I am 24/7.

41
00:01:40,057 --> 00:01:41,087
我和在监狱没什么两样
I'm still in prison.

42
00:01:41,091 --> 00:01:43,041
假释期的追踪器
Parole bracelet?

43
00:01:43,044 --> 00:01:45,004
我能把这玩意拿下来
I can get this off.

44
00:01:45,097 --> 00:01:46,097
你不能割断追踪器
You can't cut bracelet.

45
00:01:47,001 --> 00:01:48,011
我也没打算那样做
I'm not gonna cut the bracelet.

46
00:01:50,067 --> 00:01:51,091
看你都干了些什么
What the hell have you done?!

47
00:01:51,094 --> 00:01:53,024
够了  到此为止吧 
That's it, this is over.

48
00:01:53,027 --> 00:01:55,041
杰克  对你来说结束了  而我才刚开始
Maybe for you, Jack, but I'm just getting started.

49
00:01:58,042 --> 00:02:02,098
以下事件发生于晚上八点到九点
The following takes place between 8:00 P.M. and 9:00 P.M.

50
00:02:03,093 --> 00:02:07,059
卡米斯坦伊斯兰共和国

51
00:02:07,090 --> 00:02:10,097
今天的首都  忠于哈桑总统的军队

52
00:02:11,024 --> 00:02:16,053
抓捕了很多意图颠覆政权的叛徒

53
00:02:17,004 --> 00:02:20,007
政府的各个部门中都揪出了嫌犯

54
00:02:23,072 --> 00:02:25,015
我还以为你不是死了就是给抓了呢
I thought you were dead or captured.

55
00:02:26,001 --> 00:02:28,007
我好不容易才摆脱他们的追捕
It took me this long to get clear.

56
00:02:28,011 --> 00:02:29,041
我和巴扎耶夫在一起
I'm with Bazhaev.

57
00:02:29,044 --> 00:02:30,097
去他妈的巴扎耶夫
To hell with Bazhaev!

58
00:02:31,001 --> 00:02:33,041
都是因为他  我们的努力才付之东流
Everything we have worked for, it's all over because of him.

59
00:02:33,074 --> 00:02:35,017
你这就言之过早了  将军
It's not over, General.

60
00:02:35,021 --> 00:02:36,051
当然都玩完了
Of course it is!

61
00:02:36,054 --> 00:02:37,091
你的哥哥还活着
Your brother is still alive,

62
00:02:37,094 --> 00:02:40,051
你的元首梦也破碎了
and your plan to replace him as head of state is finished.

63
00:02:40,054 --> 00:02:44,010
现在他的卫队正全城搜捕我们
Now his security forces are rounding up our people all over the city.

64
00:02:44,077 --> 00:02:47,047
就在五分钟前  阿米礼将军
General Amiri was just pulled from his home five minutes ago,

65
00:02:47,051 --> 00:02:49,027
在家人面前被逮捕了
in front of his wife and children.

66
00:02:49,031 --> 00:02:51,075
美国人不会同意他这样继续下去
Look, the Americans won't let him continue.

67
00:02:51,075 --> 00:02:53,069
会指责他侵犯了人权
They'll accuse him of human rights violations

68
00:02:53,069 --> 00:02:55,071
并以退出和平会谈为威胁
and threaten to pull out of the peace talks.

69
00:02:55,074 --> 00:02:57,044
等浓缩铀一到手
Once we have the uranium,

70
00:02:57,047 --> 00:02:59,064
我哥哥就不再是问题了
my brother will become irrelevant anyway.

71
00:02:59,067 --> 00:03:01,054
你被人四处追捕
You are being hunted like an animal.

72
00:03:01,057 --> 00:03:03,017
怎么把浓缩铀拿到手
How do you expect to get the uranium?

73
00:03:03,021 --> 00:03:04,057
巴扎耶夫可以帮我们拿到手
Bazhaev can deliver it to us,

74
00:03:04,061 --> 00:03:07,074
但我需要先把钱打到他的账户上
but first I need payment wired to his account.

75
00:03:11,001 --> 00:03:12,001
没事的
It's all right.

76
00:03:12,004 --> 00:03:13,037
谢谢
Mm. Thank you.

