00:03:35,040 --> 00:03:37,064
爸爸  弗农山有个诊所
Papa, there's a clinic in Mt. Vernon.

84
00:03:37,067 --> 00:03:40,011
我在那边找到了一个能治疗他的医生
I found a doctor who can treat him.

85
00:03:40,014 --> 00:03:41,044
我们不是说好了吗
We have been through this.

86
00:03:41,047 --> 00:03:42,077
不找医生
No doctors.

87
00:03:42,081 --> 00:03:44,047
没错  但是这个医生有家小
Yes, but this one has a family.

88
00:03:44,051 --> 00:03:46,047
我知道他们的名字和住址
I know where they are, I know their names.

89
00:03:46,051 --> 00:03:48,051
我保证让他守口如瓶
I'll make sure he keeps his mouth shut.

90
00:03:48,054 --> 00:03:51,044
你也能保证诊所里其他人不会发现吗
And you can guarantee no one else in this clinic will find out?

91
00:03:51,047 --> 00:03:52,094
保证别的医生  护士  任何人不泄密吗
Another doctor, a nurse, no one?

92
00:03:54,021 --> 00:03:57,011
当局知道核原料的事情
The authorities know about the nuclear material

93
00:03:57,014 --> 00:03:58,051
或者不久就会知道了
or they will soon enough,

94
00:03:58,054 --> 00:03:59,091
他们会四处查找的
and they'll be looking everywhere.

95
00:03:59,094 --> 00:04:03,027
把欧力格送医会引狼入室
Putting Oleg in a clinic would lead them right to us.

96
00:04:03,031 --> 00:04:06,087
如果我们不赶紧把他送医的话他会死的
He's going to die if we don't get him help.

97
00:04:06,091 --> 00:04:09,071
那让他死好了
Then he's going to die.

98
00:04:12,094 --> 00:04:15,014
但让他如此孤单地死在
But alone like this?

99
00:04:15,017 --> 00:04:18,037
厨房后面冰冷的屋子里吗
In a cold room behind the kitchen?

100
00:04:18,041 --> 00:04:20,037
他是我的弟弟  爸爸
He's my brother, Papa,

101
00:04:21,071 --> 00:04:22,076
也是您的儿子啊
and he's your son.

102
00:04:29,085 --> 00:04:30,097
好吧
All right.

103
00:04:31,001 --> 00:04:32,034
把他带去郊区别墅
Take him to the country house.

104
00:04:32,037 --> 00:04:34,047
乌兰娜会照顾他的
Ulana will look after him.

105
00:04:35,024 --> 00:04:36,019
谢谢  爸爸
Thank you, Papa.

106
00:04:39,095 --> 00:04:41,001
什么事
What is it?

107
00:04:41,004 --> 00:04:43,031
法哈德找你
Farhad is asking for you.

108
00:04:53,007 --> 00:04:54,074
有新消息吗
You have news for me?

109
00:04:54,077 --> 00:04:56,011
是的
Yes.

110
00:04:56,014 --> 00:04:58,077
钱马上就汇到你的账户了
The money will be transferred to your account shortly.

111
00:04:58,081 --> 00:05:01,051
什么时候给我浓缩铀棒
When can I take possession of the rods?

112
00:05:01,054 --> 00:05:04,034
钱一到就给你
As soon as we have the money.

113
00:05:04,085 --> 00:05:07,014
给我五个小时
Five hours.

114
00:05:07,017 --> 00:05:08,012
很好
Good.

115
00:05:08,087 --> 00:05:11,064
我帮你打发时间吧
I'll help you pass the time.

116
00:05:19,087 --> 00:05:21,094
有特殊偏好吗
You have a preference?

117
00:05:22,044 --> 00:05:23,097
没
No.

118
00:05:24,001 --> 00:05:25,081
那两个都归你吧
Then take both.

119
00:05:38,058 --> 00:05:40,061
他还在出血
He's still bleeding out.

120
00:05:40,064 --> 00:05:43,047
这个应该可以止血的
This should cauterize the wound.

121
00:05:46,097 --> 00:05:48,061
好了
Okay, it's working.

122
00:05:51,068 --> 00:05:52,043
你打给谁
Who are you calling?

123
00:05:52,081 --> 00:05:54,011
-黑斯廷斯  -为什么
- Hastings. - Why?

124
00:05:54,014 --> 00:05:55,041
我要让他取消这次行动
Because I'm shutting this operation down.

125
00:05:55,044 --> 00:05:56,081
你还没准备好出外勤  这就是证据
You shouldn't be in the field, and this proves it.

126
00:05:56,084 --> 00:05:58,007
只能赌上这一把了  杰克
This was the only play, Jack.

127
00:05:58,011 --> 00:05:59,031
换你也会这么做的
You would've done the same thing.

128
00:05:59,034 --> 00:06:00,084
放手一搏的目的是让他合作
The play was to get him to cooperate.

129
00:06:00,087 --> 00:06:02,081
-他会合作的  -你怎么知道
- He will cooperate. - How do you figure?

130
00:06:02,084 --> 00:06:04,041
我了解这帮人  杰克
Look, I know these guys, Jack.

131
00:06:04,044 --> 00:06:07,054
兹亚除了幼女之外  最爱的就是钱了
The only thing that Ziya likes more than 13-year-old girls is money.

132
00:06:07,057 --> 00:06:09,031
让他赚这么一大笔  他死都愿意
He'd have butchered himself for a score like this.

133
00:06:09,034 --> 00:06:10,097
是啊  但黑斯廷斯仍需要知道真相
Yeah, well, Hastings still needs to know the truth.

134
00:06:11,062 --> 00:06:13,064
就是你状态一点也不稳定
That you're unstable!

135
00:06:19,054 --> 00:06:23,071
听着  我不怪你
Look... I don't blame you

136
00:06:23,074 --> 00:06:25,047
毕竟你经历了这么多坎坷
after everything you've been through,

137
00:06:25,051 --> 00:06:27,097
但是你不适合这个任务
but you are not fit for this mission.

138
00:06:28,057 --> 00:06:30,077
我的确有过一段艰辛坎坷的日子
I went through a rough patch, yeah,

139
00:06:30,081 --> 00:06:32,061
但我从低谷中走了出来
but I came out on the other side.

140
00:06:32,064 --> 00:06:34,034
我可不这么认为
And I don't think you have.

141
00:06:36,024 --> 00:06:37,017
不管怎么说  
The bottom line is,

142
00:06:37,017 --> 00:06:40,011
我还是帮你们夺取浓缩铀的最佳人选
I'm still the best chance that anyone has of intercepting that uranium,

143
00:06:40,014 --> 00:06:41,064
我现在就能做到
and I can do it now.

144
00:06:47,034 --> 00:06:49,067
现在怎样  你还打电话吗
So, what's it going to be, you making that phone call or what?

145
00:07:00,018 --> 00:07:01,020
他快醒了  杰克
He's waking up, Jack.

146
00:07:01,020 --> 00:07:02,030
赶紧决定吧
Better make up your mind.

147
00:07:08,096 --> 00:07:09,091
好吧
Fine.

148
00:07:09,094 --> 00:07:12,031
看你能问出什么来
You see what you can get out of him.

149
00:07:12,034 --> 00:07:16,067
但别忘了  我都听得见
But don't forget, I'm listening.

150
00:07:31,077 --> 00:07:33,027
闭嘴  兹亚
Shut up, Ziya.

151
00:07:35,024 --> 00:07:36,037
我们一出去就给你止痛药
You'll get your painkillers as soon as we get out of here.

152
00:07:36,041 --> 00:07:38,061
-你都做了些什么  -我帮你拿下了追踪器
- What did you do?! - I got the bracelet off,

153
00:07:38,064 --> 00:07:40,027
帮了你一个忙啊
all right, I did you a favor.

154
00:07:40,031 --> 00:07:43,031
你这个疯婊子  把我拇指切掉了
You crazy bitch! You cut off thumb!

155
00:07:43,034 --> 00:07:44,084
木已成舟
Look, what's done is done.

156
00:07:44,087 --> 00:07:47,017
要么你在这像婴儿一样哭嚎抱怨
You can either stay here and whine about it like a baby,

157
00:07:47,021 --> 00:07:49,067
要么你跟我来大赚一笔
or you can come with me and be a rich man.

158
00:07:49,071 --> 00:07:53,044
我可以从总收入里给你分成
Look, I'm willing to give you a point on this deal off the top.

159
00:07:53,047 --> 00:07:56,031
是很大的一笔钱啊  兹亚
It's a lot of money, Ziya.

160
00:07:56,034 --> 00:07:57,064
多少
How much?

161
00:07:57,067 --> 00:07:59,014
250万
Two-and-a-half million.

162
00:07:59,085 --> 00:08:02,021
事成后  300万也说不定
Maybe three when it's all done.

163
00:08:03,020 --> 00:08:04,018
200万
Two million?

164
00:08:05,011 --> 00:08:06,064
真的吗
You're serious?

165
00:08:06,067 --> 00:08:08,007
你说呢
You tell me.

166
00:08:11,041 --> 00:08:13,058
我把这笔买卖介绍给瓦德米尔
I take this deal to Vladimir,

167
00:08:13,058 --> 00:08:15,041
如果是骗局  你知道后果吗
and it's not real, you know what happens?!

168
00:08:15,044 --> 00:08:17,034
如果是骗局我又何必过来
Why would I be here if this wasn't real?!

169
00:08:19,024 --> 00:08:20,061
算了  兹亚
Fine, forget it, Ziya.

170
00:08:20,064 --> 00:08:21,091
我会自己找到瓦德米尔的
I'll find Vladimir my own way.

171
00:08:21,094 --> 00:08:23,031
不  等等
No, wait!

172
00:08:26,077 --> 00:08:29,054
我不知道他的确切位置
I don't know where he is exactly,

173
00:08:29,057 --> 00:08:30,091
不过知道他可能去哪
but where he might be.

174
00:08:30,094 --> 00:08:31,049
说
Tell me.

175
00:08:32,077 --> 00:08:34,097
现在不是时候  我一会儿带你去
No, I'll take you there myself.

176
00:08:35,001 --> 00:08:36,034
你有车吗
You have a car?

177
00:08:36,037 --> 00:08:37,077
我有辆货车  停在后面
I have truck; it's parked out back.

178
00:08:37,081 --> 00:08:39,021
好吧  我来开
All right, I'll drive.

179
00:08:39,073 --> 00:08:40,041
起来
Come on!

180
00:08:42,084 --> 00:08:43,037
喂
Yeah?

181
00:08:43,041 --> 00:08:44,087
杰克  我刚刚在背景资料里发现
Jack, I just found out in my background check

182
00:08:44,087 --> 00:08:46,071
兹亚还有个假释官
that Ziya has a probation officer.

183
